00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:54,510
and when he was confronted over
one case, he got pretty annoyed.

251
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:58,510
When the body of Henry Glover
was found in this burnedout car,

252
00:14:58,560 --> 00:15:02,540
