being responsible for his death.

253
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:07,340
But Coroner Minyard did not
classify it as a homicide

254
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:10,390
and so there was
no criminal investigation.

255
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:15,340
A burned-up body
inside a burned-out car?

256
00:15:16,450 --> 00:15:19,560
- Behind a police station?
