outsourcing work
to private contractors.

321
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:08,640
This is where this story
gets incredible.

322
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:12,630
Let me introduce you to one
terrible example of this.

323
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:16,620
In Missouri and Kansas, a number
of coroners offices wound up hiring

324
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:20,630
